This paper deals with forwarding strategies for fragmented datagrams in the IoT, which is a topic related to network protocols and communication in computer networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses reliability and latency, which are topics related to security and cryptography (cs.CR), information theory (cs.IT), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since the focus of the paper is on networking and communication, these categories are less likely than cs.NI.
